      "comment": "SCOTT WEDNESDAY (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (19.86) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Has ability and looks hard to stop. PRINCE OF PANAMA (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (19.61) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Bold showing expected. PAW ZEVA (8) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at Goulburn over 350m behind Nitro Venom (20.27) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Great chance to atone. HIBIKI BLUE (2) can sneak into the finish.",
